---

<BaseLayout title="Favorite Artists">
    <h1>Who inspires my work?</h1>
    <p>
        I am but a prism directing a combination of the light of those in my lightcone, so I have been inspired by many, many
        artists. Here I'm going to largely focus on those that have been key to my growth as an artist and those that have 
        gotten me through life. Click on the images for links to my favorite works by each artist.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Musicians</h2>
    <div class="artist-grid">
        {musicians.map((artist) => (
            <a href={artist.profileUrl} class="artist-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <div class="artist-item">
                    <div class="artist-card">
                       <img src={artist.imageUrl} alt={artist.name} class="artist-image"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="artist-name">{artist.name}</div>
                </div>
            </a>
        ))}
    </div>

    <h2>Visual Artists</h2>
    <div class="artist-grid">
        {visualArtists.map((artist) => (
             <a href={artist.profileUrl} class="artist-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <div class="artist-item">
                    <div class="artist-card">
                         <img src={artist.imageUrl} alt={artist.name} class="artist-image"/>
                    </div>
